<item>
            <title>[SOLR-8137] Core Admin -&gt; Swap - minor issues with &quot;and:&quot; field</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-8137</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In a New UI click &apos;Core Admin&apos;, then &apos;Swap&apos;. There is an empty default field in &quot;and:&quot; option. And you can also swap the same core (like &apos;core1&apos; and &apos;core1&apos;) which is not good.&lt;br/&gt;
In Original UI there are only valid cores are shown (i.e. no empty and no current core is not shown), and a first valid core is selected by default.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
