                            <comment id="14946792" author="arconamagi" created="Wed, 7 Oct 2015 12:48:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here is a patch to make a New UI behaviour similar to Original UI:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;no empty option is shown (if there are at least 2 cores),&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;only cores which differs from current core are listed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Note: instead of filtering of $scope.corelist (I don&apos;t know how do you plan to use it, and the name &apos;corelist&apos; means no filtering applied to it) I&apos;ve created a new filtered list of cores to swap with ($scope.swapCoreList).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
