                            <comment id="14946799" author="upayavira" created="Wed, 7 Oct 2015 12:54:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for this report. I hope it is resolved now.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you are not working directly out of SVN, please try replacing these two files:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/viewvc/lucene/dev/branches/branch_5x/solr/webapp/web/js/angular/controllers/cores.js?view=co&amp;amp;revision=1707284&amp;amp;content-type=text%2Fplain&amp;amp;pathrev=1707284&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/viewvc/lucene/dev/branches/branch_5x/solr/webapp/web/js/angular/controllers/cores.js?view=co&amp;amp;revision=1707284&amp;amp;content-type=text%2Fplain&amp;amp;pathrev=1707284&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
