&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-8137&quot; title=&quot;Core Admin -&amp;gt; Swap - minor issues with &amp;quot;and:&amp;quot; field&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-8137&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-8137&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; Use swapCorelist rather than otherCorelist&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14946813" author="upayavira" created="Wed, 7 Oct 2015 13:02:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just seen your patch - It seems we both did basically the same thing at the same time - I was too quick.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve switched it to use your naming, swapCorelist was a better name than otherCorelist.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the patch!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
